hello

Got a decent little 35-50ish second map. Originally, I wanted this to be longer and more difficult. However, I am about to have my first child & I am pushing to finish my bachelors. I probably won't have a lot of time or motivation to sink into it, but I am moderately happy with the map and didn't want to sit on it.

I did not obtain any testers sadly, but if there are any major things I need to fix then reach out to me and I will do it.

Theme from/inspired from Vay
KZ bonus from Vay as well.
